Date: Fri, 17 Jan 2014 17:28:35 GMT</programlisting></para>
                </listitem>
            </itemizedlist>
            <para>The <code>Created (201)</code> response code indicates a
                successful write.</para>
            <para>If the request times out, the operation returns the
